narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Professional Medical Corp is a Durable Medical Equipment & Medical Supplies provider based in Seattle, WA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $18.7M in Medicaid payments across 510K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $18.7M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
